{"tid":1499582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大學生於西藏被扣查 (Campus TV, HKUSU)","createTime":"2019-08-23T18:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T18:35:28.000Z","uid":287719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20d9d8e44c04901db7b8088bcfc5a1caa830bb26","tid":1499582,"uid":287719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:26:51.000Z","msg":"//【即時新聞】港大學生於西藏被扣查<br />\n<br />\n（0000更新）片段已於微博上刪除<br />\n<br />\n（1150更新）港大學生會署理會長黃程峰指港大校方及學生會經已聯絡同學家屬，而學生會亦有向律師團隊聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n微博流傳片段，指有香港大學生在西藏珠穆朗瑪峰大本營被公安扣查，而片段中有正就讀香港大學的學生。消息指有團友曾於社交專頁發佈「光復香港 時代革命」或其他支持香港民主自由的字句而被扣查。如觀眾有任何消息請向本台聯絡。//<br />\n<br />\n原Post: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2411295418939140?s=1851786966&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F2411295418939140%3Fs%3D1851786966%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmwa&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=19e5dce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/2411295418939140?s=1851786966&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa</a>"},{"pid":"5baf394733950b1ee7d541715f6cde5346c1e89e","tid":1499582,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n借位<br />\n<br />\n被控義士們依家點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1499004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1499004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba2a7f84834de3603a066f9815ead06ae4235f68","tid":1499582,"uid":287719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Epen9mq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpen9mq.jpg&h=c133a9e